"<h1>頁面源代碼</h1>\n\n<div class=\"page-source\">\n\t[[include <a href=\"http://scp-zh-tr.wikidot.com/component:scp-meta-title-hiding\">:scp-zh-tr:component:scp-meta-title-hiding</a> css-style=classic]]<br />\n[[include <a href=\"http://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/component:pride-highlighter\">:scp-wiki:component:pride-highlighter</a> |inc-s9-bi= --]]]<br />\n<br />\n[[module CSS]]<br />\n/* HEADER */<br />\n#header h1 a{<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;display: block;<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;margin: 0;<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;padding: 80px 0 25px;<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;line-height: 0;<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;max-height: 0;<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;color: transparent;<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;background: transparent;<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;font-family: 'Verdana', Arial, sans-serif;<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;text-decoration: none;<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;text-shadow: none;<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;letter-spacing: 0.9px;<br />\n}<br />\n#header h1 a::before{<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;content: &quot;誤傳部&quot;;<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;color: white;<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;letter-spacing: -0.02em;<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;text-shadow: 3px 3px 5px black;<br />\n}<br />\n#header h2 span{<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;display: block;<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;margin: 0;<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;padding: 19px 0;<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;line-height: 0;<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;max-height: 0;<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;font-weight: bold;<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;color: transparent;<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;text-shadow: none;<br />\n}<br />\n#header h2 span::before{<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;content: '施策普適傳譬';<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;color: white;<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;text-shadow: 1px 1px 1px black;<br />\n}<br />\n[[/module]]<br />\n<br />\n[[include <a href=\"/credit:start\">credit:start</a>]]<br />\n**原著：** [[*user Henzoid]]、[[*user Westrin]]<br />\n**譯者：** [[*user edward-knave]]<br />\n**原題：** SCP-4098 - S-C-P, easy as 19-3-16!<br />\n**譯題：** SCP-4098 - S-C-P，視詞篇順暢排19-3-16<br />\n**原文：** https://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/scp-4098<br />\n[[include <a href=\"/credit:end\">credit:end</a>]]<br />\n<br />\n[[table style=&quot;border: none; width: 100%;&quot;]]<br />\n[[row]]<br />\n[[cell]]<br />\n[[size 125%]]**守藏品：** SCP-4098<br />\n[[/size]]<br />\n[[/cell]]<br />\n[[cell style=&quot;text-align: right;&quot;]]<br />\n[[size 125%]]**###990000|授察憑 4/4098##**[[/size]]<br />\n[[/cell]]<br />\n[[/row]]<br />\n[[row]]<br />\n[[cell]]<br />\n[[size 125%]]**設稱評：** 神讎破[[/size]]<br />\n[[/cell]]<br />\n[[cell style=&quot;text-align: right;&quot;]]<br />\n[[size 125%]]**###990000|肅藏篇##**[[/size]]<br />\n[[/cell]]<br />\n[[/row]]<br />\n[[/table]]<br />\n----<br />\n<br />\n[[div class=&quot;scp-image-block block-center&quot; style=&quot;width:100%;&quot;]]<br />\n[[image https://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-4098/scpscp.png style=&quot;width:100%;&quot; link=#]]<br />\n[[div class=&quot;scp-image-caption&quot; style=&quot;width:100%;&quot;]]<br />\nSite-94曾闢設此坪。<br />\n[[/div]]<br />\n[[/div]]<br />\n<br />\n----<br />\n**收此偏恃策篇：** SCP-4098受儲配擅稱，聘三乘徬雙藏屏士長陪。雙層鋪實彩普斯澄璞鎖儲品所，成闢實存屏。<br />\n<br />\nSCP-4098事常屏守出破SCP-4098-1傷察品式持否。審查篇說策頗生瞠睥，時測徬SCP-4098-1所藏評，遂持平。<br />\n<br />\n伺策屏倏衝破，仕才跑適[[[domc-hub|傳譬師]]]揣盤思策品。<br />\n<br />\n**述此偏：** SCP-4098屬曾旁Site-94處鋪設層磐。時曾排Site-94澈剖傷察品式、[[span class=&quot;ruby&quot;]]超普識傳派[[span class=&quot;rt&quot;]]Paramemetics[[/span]][[/span]]。<br />\n<br />\nSCP-4098似存陪Site-94處披斯儲品所充坪，使傳篇隨篡偏適辭品。屬詞駢受操盤，說辭拼聲徹憑SCP順重篇。<br />\n<br />\nSite-94藏品適才配Site-96存鋪，遂成否。Site-94策屏術超迫Site-96存配。傷察品式測破術出品所從評事長憑。<br />\n<br />\nSCP-4098-1屬稱配守藏辟式，傳篇守重批遂拆破。生承丕識，初曝、視、察破SCP-4098-1，倏成匹屍寸殍。<br />\n<br />\n隨策品「[[span class=&quot;ruby&quot;]]蘇礎磐師糙樸[[span class=&quot;rt&quot;]]Socrates' Crass Purity[[/span]][[/span]]」善處，瞥SCP-4098始篡篇、掃辭排，受此迫，識澈剖士萃破神誠，屏所湊排SCP所處配室出平舍常朋所察評。守倉配帥從霹速傳片書，出旁屬參憑。SCP-4098-1閃察屏識殘篇遂藏，憑Site-94出品收藏配適除否。<br />\n<br />\n**隨從篇：**<br />\n&gt; //稍初憑仕持捧Site-94曾配收儲品，受挫迫，說此篇：「ㄙ為ㄘ甚ㄆ麼ㄙ你ㄘ們ㄆ就ㄙ不ㄘ能ㄆ夠ㄙ這ㄘ樣ㄆ子ㄙ說ㄘ話ㄆ啊？」//<br />\n&gt; <br />\n&gt; //隨此判：屍陳排十乘徬雙除撇三，察評士懲破誓才僕，肅斥旁屬疵紕。//<br />\n[[=]]<br />\n[[div class=&quot;footer-wikiwalk-nav&quot;]]<br />\n----<br />\n« [[[SCP-4097]]] | SCP-4098 | [[[SCP-4099]]] »<br />\n[[/div]]<br />\n[[/=]]<br />\n<br />\n[[include <a href=\"http://scp-zh-tr.wikidot.com/component:license-box\">:scp-zh-tr:component:license-box</a><br />\n|lang=EN<br />\n|author=Westrin及Henzoid]]<br />\n=====<br />\n&gt; **檔案名稱：** scpscp.png<br />\n&gt; **圖像名稱：** Landsman Research Facility, Brandeis University<br />\n&gt; **圖像作者：** Kenneth C. Zirkel<br />\n&gt; **圖像授權協議：** CC BY-SA 4.0<br />\n&gt; **圖源連結：** [https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:Landsman_Research_Facility,_Brandeis_University.jpg 維基共享資源]<br />\n=====<br />\n[[include <a href=\"http://scp-zh-tr.wikidot.com/component:license-box-end\">:scp-zh-tr:component:license-box-end</a>]]\n</div>\n"